_json.gridTitle: Ultimate Guide To Needle Felting - Full of needle felting ideas, tutorials, and getting started!
_json.description: A fabulous craft blog packed full of how to needle felt advice for complete beginners and beyond. You will find needle felting videos, needle felting tutorials and all my favourite needle felting hacks. Crafts as therapy is my favourite subject and it doesn't get more therapeutic or easy than needle felting. It is also completely addictive! #needlefeltingideas #howtoneedlefelt #needlefeltingtutorials #needlefeltinghacks
